nodes.text: Immi Danoo was a patron of the Outlander Club on Coruscant. She was friends with Nyrat Agira and Rosha Vess.

Immi Danoo was a great woman wearing very light clothing during her visit to the Outlander where she met with Rosha Vess and Nyrat Agira. Danoo wore a top and a mini skirt. As one of the three, she did not wear tattoos on her belly of the Zealots of Psusan.
